1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:42,729 --> 00:01:47,289
[My Wife is A Thief]

3
00:01:47,810 --> 00:01:52,270
[Episode 23]

4
00:02:12,190 --> 00:02:14,290
You're very skilled in this.

5
00:02:14,990 --> 00:02:17,230
I've done it for my mother before.

6
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,620
Was it for your mother

7
00:02:19,790 --> 00:02:21,550
or for a lady?

8
00:02:23,110 --> 00:02:23,670
See?

9
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:25,860
Even if I did it well,

10
00:02:26,070 --> 00:02:27,530
I still got scolded by you.

11
00:02:27,610 --> 00:02:29,390
I wouldn't have done it if I had known earlier.

12
00:02:29,390 --> 00:02:31,250
What? Are you getting tired of it?

13
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:33,160
I dare not.

14
00:02:47,110 --> 00:02:47,790
Don't move.

15
00:02:51,470 --> 00:02:52,350
What's this?

16
00:02:53,230 --> 00:02:55,430
I bought it when I went out this morning.

17
00:02:55,430 --> 00:02:58,230
I noticed that I haven't given you a gift in a while.

18
00:02:59,510 --> 00:03:01,840
Let's consider this as a token of our love.

19
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:12,400
Do you like it?

20
00:03:12,830 --> 00:03:13,510
Yes.

21
00:03:14,190 --> 00:03:15,160
Good for you, Darling.

22
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:16,470
You're getting better in romance.

23
00:03:16,470 --> 00:03:17,990
It's because you are a good teacher, Honey.

24
00:03:17,990 --> 00:03:19,110
Don't be too proud of yourself.

25
00:03:19,110 --> 00:03:19,950
Keep working.

26
00:03:25,510 --> 00:03:28,570
However, this can only be considered an ordinary gift.

27
00:03:31,150 --> 00:03:34,150
As for the token of love, you've already given it to me.

28
00:03:39,590 --> 00:03:41,670
It's really like "the spring breeze bringing a message,

29
00:03:41,670 --> 00:03:42,990
with a precious jade as the matchmaker."

30
00:03:42,990 --> 00:03:45,100
I never thought that the jade pendant my father left me

31
00:03:45,100 --> 00:03:46,960
would bring me such good fortune.

32
00:03:47,030 --> 00:03:48,310
But speaking of which,

33
00:03:48,590 --> 00:03:50,550
I agreed to marry you in place of Su Jinzhen for two reasons.

34
00:03:50,550 --> 00:03:51,230
Firstly,

35
00:03:51,230 --> 00:03:53,490
it was because you trapped me in the room.

36
00:03:53,550 --> 00:03:54,990
That was because I figured out

37
00:03:54,990 --> 00:03:57,350
that you committed the crime with the golden cricket.

38
00:03:57,350 --> 00:03:58,310
And secondly,

39
00:03:58,440 --> 00:03:59,790
it was because my Master ordered me

40
00:03:59,790 --> 00:04:01,070
to steal this jade pendant.

41
00:04:01,070 --> 00:04:01,990
Otherwise,

42
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:04,280
with one of us being an official and the other a thief,

43
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:07,080
we probably would never have met in this lifetime.

44
00:04:09,270 --> 00:04:11,780
Your Master told you to steal the jade pendant?

45
00:04:11,780 --> 00:04:12,430
Why?

46
00:04:12,650 --> 00:04:13,560
She said

47
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:16,269
this jade pendant is related to the flood case in Taizhou.

48
00:04:16,269 --> 00:04:17,730
The flood case in Taizhou?

49
00:04:19,910 --> 00:04:21,440
So the mastermind behind it

50
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:22,830
must be Duke Su.

51
00:04:23,390 --> 00:04:24,110
But why would he

52
00:04:24,110 --> 00:04:26,510
be interested in my father's jade pendant?

53
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,460
Could there be some secret

54
00:04:29,270 --> 00:04:30,730
behind this jade pendant?

55
00:04:40,790 --> 00:04:42,909
How about we go ask my Master?

56
00:04:47,550 --> 00:04:48,230
Master,

57
00:04:48,390 --> 00:04:51,390
this is the jade pendant you've been asking me to find.

58
00:04:56,710 --> 00:04:57,310
Rong,

59
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,470
since you have already got this jade pendant,

60
00:05:00,470 --> 00:05:02,470
why didn't you give it to me earlier?

61
00:05:02,590 --> 00:05:04,120
How could that be possible?

62
00:05:04,230 --> 00:05:06,670
Xu Muchen just gave me this jade pendant recently.

63
00:05:06,670 --> 00:05:07,310
Right?

64
00:05:08,710 --> 00:05:09,280
Yes.

65
00:05:14,630 --> 00:05:15,320
Forget it.

66
00:05:16,110 --> 00:05:16,800
Muchen.

67
00:05:17,340 --> 00:05:18,790
For you, Rong would rather conceal

68
00:05:18,790 --> 00:05:20,730
the existence of the jade pendant from me.

69
00:05:20,730 --> 00:05:22,660
It shows how much she cares for you.

70
00:05:22,810 --> 00:05:24,500
You must not disappoint her.

71
00:05:25,310 --> 00:05:26,970
Master, don't worry about it.

72
00:05:32,909 --> 00:05:33,900
Master.

73
00:05:34,350 --> 00:05:36,550
do you know why Duke Su wanted us

74
00:05:36,550 --> 00:05:38,550
to find this jade pendant back then?

75
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:41,630
At that time, I was only commanded

76
00:05:41,630 --> 00:05:43,740
to tell you to steal this jade pendant.

77
00:05:43,740 --> 00:05:45,030
As for its purpose,

78
00:05:45,030 --> 00:05:46,159
I really don't know.

79
00:05:47,590 --> 00:05:48,250
However...

80
00:05:48,990 --> 00:05:49,909
What?

81
00:05:51,590 --> 00:05:53,360
However, Xu Chengsi, Lord Xu,

82
00:05:53,500 --> 00:05:54,790
not only had extraordinary intelligence

83
00:05:54,790 --> 00:05:56,150
but also understood the technique

84
00:05:56,150 --> 00:05:57,550
of crafting mechanisms.

85
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,130
You see, the design of this jade pendant

86
00:06:00,130 --> 00:06:02,530
is slightly different from ordinary ones.

87
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:09,080
It does seem different.

88
00:06:10,750 --> 00:06:11,750
This jade pendant

89
00:06:12,590 --> 00:06:15,390
looks more like a key to unlocking some mechanism.

90
00:06:17,430 --> 00:06:18,110
My father had evidence

91
00:06:18,110 --> 00:06:20,070
of Duke Su planting Moon Star Herb.

92
00:06:20,990 --> 00:06:22,920
So this jade pendant must be the key

93
00:06:23,550 --> 00:06:25,920
to unlock the whereabouts of the hidden evidence.

94
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,390
If it's a key,

95
00:06:27,390 --> 00:06:28,650
then where is the door?

96
00:06:29,910 --> 00:06:31,160
Look at this side.

97
00:06:34,659 --> 00:06:36,460
Look. Can you see the difference

98
00:06:36,750 --> 00:06:39,750
between this plum blossom pattern and ordinary ones?

99
00:06:40,510 --> 00:06:42,710
This plum blossom has broken patterns.

100
00:06:44,950 --> 00:06:46,430
If these patterns

101
00:06:46,630 --> 00:06:48,630
were intentionally made by Lord Xu,

102
00:06:48,990 --> 00:06:50,750
he must have left some clues.

103
00:06:52,990 --> 00:06:53,790
Plum Blossom?

104
00:06:57,310 --> 00:06:58,390
Take this.

105
00:06:59,890 --> 00:07:00,180
[Plum Blossom Collection]

106
00:07:01,390 --> 00:07:02,040
Mother,

107
00:07:02,830 --> 00:07:03,830
what is this?

108
00:07:05,150 --> 00:07:08,750
This is a plum blossom album your father made before his passing.

109
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:11,100
Before he went to Taizhou, he said

110
00:07:11,830 --> 00:07:14,290
the peach blossoms there were in full bloom,

111
00:07:14,590 --> 00:07:15,390
and he planned to bring back

112
00:07:15,390 --> 00:07:17,390
a petal for me to tuck into the album,

113
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:20,320
and to draw a Peach Blossom Collection.

114
00:07:21,030 --> 00:07:22,230
Could it be that book?

115
00:07:23,470 --> 00:07:24,110
Master,

116
00:07:24,170 --> 00:07:25,700
we're going over there now.

117
00:07:47,710 --> 00:07:49,110
Have you found anything?

118
00:07:49,230 --> 00:07:50,510
Mother said this book

119
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:53,640
was left to her by Father when he was in Taizhou.

120
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:55,560
But all the drawings in it are plum blossoms.

121
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:57,820
I didn't pay much attention to it before.

122
00:07:58,030 --> 00:08:00,160
If there is some hidden meaning behind

123
00:08:00,710 --> 00:08:02,840
the plum blossom on that jade pendant,

124
00:08:03,870 --> 00:08:04,950
then this album...

125
00:08:09,790 --> 00:08:11,750
The principle of the Nine Palaces requires the spirit tortoise to decipher.

126
00:08:11,750 --> 00:08:14,550
Two and Four are shoulders, Six and Eight are feet.

127
00:08:14,630 --> 00:08:16,870
Three on the left, Seven on the right, Nine above, and One below.

128
00:08:16,870 --> 00:08:18,400
Five resides in the center.

129
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,660
Gathering all the arts of divination

130
00:08:20,660 --> 00:08:22,590
and all the ingenious techniques.

131
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:38,350
The Diagram of Gen.

132
00:08:38,350 --> 00:08:40,750
It means Mountain among the five elements.

133
00:08:44,110 --> 00:08:45,240
The Diagram of Qian.

134
00:08:45,470 --> 00:08:47,200
It means northwest direction.

135
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:49,110
What place is that?

136
00:08:52,630 --> 00:08:54,630
The northwest part of the mountain.

137
00:08:56,630 --> 00:08:58,090
The Peach Blossom Valley.

138
00:08:58,870 --> 00:08:59,870
It looks like Muchen has deciphered

139
00:08:59,870 --> 00:09:01,310
the clues left by Lord Xu.

140
00:09:02,030 --> 00:09:02,590
You go gather

141
00:09:02,590 --> 00:09:04,650
our Watermill disciples to find him.

142
00:09:04,710 --> 00:09:07,040
I'll go to Liu Wenchu, Lord Liu, to mobilize the troops.

143
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:08,370
To mobilize the troops?

144
00:09:09,140 --> 00:09:10,230
With my many years

145
00:09:10,230 --> 00:09:11,830
of understanding of Duke Su,

146
00:09:11,830 --> 00:09:14,790
he will surely try to stop Xu Muchen from finding the evidence.

147
00:09:14,790 --> 00:09:15,990
Lord Liu's escort

148
00:09:15,990 --> 00:09:18,030
can ensure everything goes smoothly.

149
00:09:18,030 --> 00:09:18,630
Yes.

150
00:09:19,020 --> 00:09:19,710
Mumu.

151
00:09:20,510 --> 00:09:21,150
Mumu.

152
00:09:21,670 --> 00:09:22,800
I finally found you.

153
00:09:23,550 --> 00:09:24,860
Young Master Gongyang?

154
00:09:24,860 --> 00:09:26,910
You actually followed me to Taizhou?

155
00:09:26,910 --> 00:09:28,230
Are you here on orders from the Ministry of Justice

156
00:09:28,230 --> 00:09:29,690
to arrest me and my Master?

157
00:09:30,590 --> 00:09:31,110
I...

158
00:09:32,310 --> 00:09:33,470
Master, you go first.

159
00:09:33,470 --> 00:09:34,470
I'll hold him off.

160
00:09:34,630 --> 00:09:35,400
Gongyang,

161
00:09:36,110 --> 00:09:37,190
I've been deceived by villains

162
00:09:37,190 --> 00:09:38,350
and made many mistakes.

163
00:09:38,350 --> 00:09:40,390
I know my sins are grave and undeniable.

164
00:09:40,390 --> 00:09:42,310
But I do have urgent matters to attend to today

165
00:09:42,310 --> 00:09:43,670
and cannot be entangled with you.

166
00:09:43,670 --> 00:09:44,990
Let me finish my business first,

167
00:09:44,990 --> 00:09:46,990
and then you can deal with me as you wish.

168
00:09:46,990 --> 00:09:47,630
Master,

169
00:09:47,990 --> 00:09:49,520
what are you talking about?

170
00:09:49,620 --> 00:09:50,620
Gongyang Maocai,

171
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,270
If you dare to lay a finger on my Master,

172
00:09:52,270 --> 00:09:53,790
you'll have to get through me first.

173
00:09:53,790 --> 00:09:55,750
Mumu, I've resigned.

174
00:09:56,510 --> 00:09:57,440
What did you say?

175
00:09:57,880 --> 00:10:00,310
I'm just a commoner now.

176
00:10:01,540 --> 00:10:03,340
As for the Watermill's affairs,

177
00:10:04,030 --> 00:10:06,760
they have nothing to do with me, Gongyang Maocai.

178
00:10:16,070 --> 00:10:17,270
I'm Gongyang Maocai.

179
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,300
Greetings, Ms. Yu Luocha.

180
00:10:20,510 --> 00:10:21,860
Are you saying

181
00:10:23,070 --> 00:10:25,600
you're not going to be an official from now on?

182
00:10:26,470 --> 00:10:27,080
Yes.

183
00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:30,480
Xu Muchen competes with me every day.

184
00:10:30,710 --> 00:10:31,750
I'm tired of it.

185
00:10:32,190 --> 00:10:33,550
I've thought it through.

186
00:10:33,550 --> 00:10:35,110
It's better that I resigned.

187
00:10:35,110 --> 00:10:36,300
That way,

188
00:10:36,470 --> 00:10:37,930
I can live with you freely.

189
00:10:39,990 --> 00:10:41,350
Don't push it.

190
00:10:41,550 --> 00:10:43,410
I never said I would live with you.

191
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:47,070
Chat with Gongyang another day if you have anything to say.

192
00:10:47,070 --> 00:10:48,110
Muchen's investigation is obstructed,

193
00:10:48,110 --> 00:10:49,630
and he needs your help.

194
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:50,230
Yes.

195
00:10:50,790 --> 00:10:51,980
You, come with me.

196
00:10:52,310 --> 00:10:53,190
Xu Muchen?

197
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:55,490
His affairs are not my concern.

198
00:10:55,670 --> 00:10:56,310
Alright.

199
00:10:56,510 --> 00:10:57,670
Stay here and have some tea.

200
00:10:57,670 --> 00:10:58,670
I'll go by myself.

201
00:11:02,550 --> 00:11:04,150
Your affairs are my concern.

202
00:11:20,470 --> 00:11:21,870
Someone is following us.

203
00:11:22,870 --> 00:11:23,800
Don't look back.

204
00:11:24,750 --> 00:11:26,010
Is it Duke Su's person?

205
00:11:26,830 --> 00:11:29,190
Senior Moyan has already sent a message to the capital.

206
00:11:29,190 --> 00:11:30,390
Based on the distance,

207
00:11:30,390 --> 00:11:32,390
Duke Su will arrive in Taizhou soon.

208
00:11:33,230 --> 00:11:35,390
I have already informed Ms. Yu Luocha,

209
00:11:35,790 --> 00:11:37,310
asking her to take my letter

210
00:11:37,310 --> 00:11:38,830
to find Uncle Liu in Taizhou.

211
00:11:38,830 --> 00:11:39,710
What's next?

212
00:11:40,870 --> 00:11:42,110
We'll go to Peach Blossom Valley

213
00:11:42,110 --> 00:11:43,190
to lure Duke Su out.

214
00:12:07,670 --> 00:12:08,510
Your Grace,

215
00:12:08,990 --> 00:12:10,670
the person we sent has been following them all the way

216
00:12:10,670 --> 00:12:12,550
to a peach blossom forest outside the suburbs,

217
00:12:12,550 --> 00:12:14,680
where Xu Muchen's trail disappeared.

218
00:12:16,670 --> 00:12:18,000
A peach blossom forest?

219
00:12:30,150 --> 00:12:30,750
Chengsi.

220
00:12:31,830 --> 00:12:32,490
Your Grace.

221
00:12:33,230 --> 00:12:34,960
Your Grace, please take a seat.

222
00:12:35,870 --> 00:12:37,670
I want to blame you for one thing.

223
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:40,430
In Taizhou,

224
00:12:40,430 --> 00:12:42,350
there are big mansions everywhere.

225
00:12:42,350 --> 00:12:43,910
If you take a fancy to any one of them,

226
00:12:43,910 --> 00:12:45,440
you can always ask me for it.

227
00:12:45,870 --> 00:12:46,790
Why bother

228
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:49,790
building a thatched hut in the peach blossom forest?

229
00:12:49,790 --> 00:12:51,450
It is uncomfortable to live in

230
00:12:51,590 --> 00:12:52,920
and cost money to build.

231
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:56,610
Aren't you afraid that your wife will blame you when you return?

232
00:12:57,190 --> 00:12:58,370
You must be joking.

233
00:12:58,830 --> 00:13:00,110
It's just a thatched hut.

234
00:13:00,110 --> 00:13:01,570
It won't cost much silver.

235
00:13:01,630 --> 00:13:03,510
I hope you will keep it secret for me

236
00:13:03,510 --> 00:13:05,350
when you return to the capital.

237
00:13:07,190 --> 00:13:08,900
For a few pieces of silver,

238
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:11,030
your wife won't give you a hard time.

239
00:13:11,830 --> 00:13:12,970
But, Chengsi,

240
00:13:13,150 --> 00:13:14,310
if after a few years,

241
00:13:14,750 --> 00:13:16,870
you still worry about being blamed by your wife

242
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:18,830
because of a few pieces of silver,

243
00:13:19,190 --> 00:13:20,670
that won't be acceptable.

244
00:13:23,110 --> 00:13:24,910
Your Grace, you're right.

245
00:13:25,350 --> 00:13:27,230
Fortunately, my wife is from a well-off family.

246
00:13:27,230 --> 00:13:28,890
She doesn't need me to be rich.

247
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:31,430
She just wants my modest salary

248
00:13:32,230 --> 00:13:33,760
to live up to my conscience.

249
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:36,970
Well said.

250
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:39,310
If everyone in the Jing State

251
00:13:39,310 --> 00:13:41,230
were like you,

252
00:13:41,470 --> 00:13:43,790
we would have peace and prosperity throughout the country,

253
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:46,790
and the prosperity of our country would last forever.

254
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:48,950
You flattered me.

255
00:13:50,310 --> 00:13:52,440
Alright, go ahead with your business.

256
00:14:02,110 --> 00:14:04,630
Good for you, Xu Chengsi.

257
00:14:06,950 --> 00:14:07,550
Let's go.

258
00:14:43,190 --> 00:14:43,950
Is it here?

259
00:14:44,870 --> 00:14:46,390
Judging from the layout of this Peach Blossom Valley,

260
00:14:46,390 --> 00:14:47,870
it looks like my father's work.

261
00:14:47,870 --> 00:14:49,350
Let's go in and take a look.

262
00:15:06,110 --> 00:15:07,910
I'll go over there to take a look.

263
00:15:56,670 --> 00:15:57,270
Darling.

264
00:15:57,830 --> 00:15:58,430
Darling.

265
00:16:03,640 --> 00:16:05,390
Why is this niche upside down?

266
00:16:37,980 --> 00:16:38,560
Here.

267
00:17:30,290 --> 00:17:30,940
My Lord.

268
00:17:31,270 --> 00:17:31,930
We're here.

269
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:34,180
Get into the mountain.

270
00:17:34,350 --> 00:17:35,100
Search.

271
00:17:35,510 --> 00:17:36,480
Yes, My Lord.

272
00:17:36,870 --> 00:17:39,980
When you encounter Xu Muchen, execute him on the spot.

273
00:17:40,590 --> 00:17:41,190
Search!

274
